messageBody:
Adnan Ahmed wrote:
> Hi,
>
> i am new in junit and want to use in one of my project
> for testing purpose. can anyone tell me any good
> tutorial or kick start resource to learn about junit.

Google.com can find good tutorials for you. Try keywords "Junit guide".
Also, there are many good books on the topic. When you joined this
group, we sent you an e-mail with information about them.
